ASK_USER=AskUserQuestion
SKILLS_DIR=~/.claude/skills
RULES_SOURCE=`.claude/rules/*.md` and `CLAUDE.md`
DISPATCH_AGENT=Launch reviewers in parallel using Agent tool with `run_in_background=true`. Send all Agent calls in a single message for true parallelism. Use the `model` parameter to set the model tier for each subagent.
PROGRESS_TOOL=TodoWrite
FILE_DISCOVERY=For file discovery, use Glob, Grep, or MCP filesystem tools if available. Do not fall back to shell commands (find, grep) unless no dedicated tool is available.
WEB_RESEARCH=Use WebSearch to find information and WebFetch to read specific pages. Prefer official documentation over blog posts.
DISPATCH_RESEARCHER=Dispatch a research subagent using Agent tool with the researcher prompt from this skill.
